the tutorial for frontlines: fow for cracked server

------------------------------------------------------

If anybody is intrested to play this game over hamachi here a little tutorial:

-go to the gamefolderGCGameConfigDefaultInput.ini

-RightClick, Properties and untick read only

-change (on the top of the File)

[Engine.Console]
; -- Set TypeKey=SemiColon to bind mini-console to ;
TypeKey=
; -- Set ConsoleKey=Tilde to bind ~ to console
ConsoleKey=

-to

[Engine.Console]
; -- Set TypeKey=SemiColon to bind mini-console to ;
TypeKey=SemiColon
; -- Set ConsoleKey=Tilde to bind ~ to console
ConsoleKey=Tilde

-downloads hamachi : http://www.planethamachi.com/downloads.php
-start hamachi
-find a server for frontlines: http://www.planethamachi.com/net_public.php
-copy the Owner in hamachi
-start the game
-one makes a lanserver
-others open console with SemiColon
-write in open Hamchi-ip

Done!
